      • between

        public static Window between​(Duration start,
                             Duration end)
        Constructs a window between two durations based on a common instant.
        Parameters:
        start - The starting time of the window.
        end - The ending time of the window.
        Returns:
        A non-empty window if start ≤ end, or an empty window otherwise.
